296
00:30:21,710 --> 00:30:24,430
No... No...

297
00:30:24,430 --> 00:30:27,930
I...

298
00:30:27,930 --> 00:30:29,280
I...

299
00:30:31,240 --> 00:30:33,040
Qiniang.

300
